 the Contingent Expenses of the Senate|Audit and Control the Contingent Expenses of the Senate]] (Chairman: [[John Kean (New Jersey politician)|John Kean]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Canadian Relations|Canadian Relations]] (Chairman: [[Winthrop Murray Crane]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on the Census|Census]] (Chairman: [[Chester I. Long]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Civil Service|Civil Service and Retrenchment]] (Chairman: [[George C. Perkins]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Claims|Claims]] (Chairman: [[Charles W. Fulton]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Coast and Insular Survey|Coast and Insular Survey]] (Chairman: [[Samuel H. Piles]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Coast Defenses|Coast Defenses]] (Chairman: [[Philander C. Knox]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Commerce|Commerce]] (Chairman: [[William P. Frye]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Corporations Organized in the District of Columbia|Corporations Organized in the District of Columbia]] (Chairman: [[Samuel D. McEnery]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Cuban Relations|Cuban Relations]] (Chairman: [[Henry E. Burnham]])\n* [[United States Senate Select Committee on Distributing Public Revenue Among the States|Distributing Public Revenue Among the States]] (Select)\n* [[United States Senate Committee on the District of Columbia|District of Columbia]] (Chairman: [[Jacob H. Gallinger]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Education and Labor|Education and Labor]] (Chairman: [[Jonathan P. Dolliver]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Engrossed Bills|Engrossed Bills]] (Chairman: [[James H. Berry]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Enrolled Bills|Enrolled Bills]] (Chairman: [[John F. Dryden]])\n* [[United States Senate Select Committee to Establish a University in the United States|Establish a University in the United States]] (Select) (Chairman: [[James A. Hemenway]])\n* [[United States Senate Select Committee on Examin