ean Championship]]\n** '''2013''' [[File:Silver medal world centered-2.svg|16px]] [[2013 FIVB Volleyball Men's U23 World Championship|FIVB U23 World Championship]]\n** '''2015''' [[File:Silver medal with cup.svg|16px]] [[2015 FIVB Volleyball World League|FIVB World League]]\n** '''2016''' [[File:Gold medal with cup.svg|16px]] [[2016 FIVB Volleyball World League|FIVB World League]]\n** '''2017''' [[File:Bronze medal europe.svg|16px]] [[2017 Men's European Volleyball Championship|CEV European Championship]]\n** '''2019''' [[File:Gold medal europe.svg|16px]]  [[2019 Men's European Volleyball Championship|CEV European Championship]]\n\n===Individually===\n* '''2011:''' CEV U19 European Championship \u2013 Most Valuable Player\n* '''2011:''' [[2011 FIVB Volleyball Boys' U19 World Championship|FIVB U19 World Championship]] \u2013 Most Valuable Player\n* '''2011:''' [[Awards of Olympic Committee of Serbia#Young Athlete of The Year|Award of Olympic Committee]] \u2013 Young Athlete of The Year\n* '''2011:''' Young Athlete of The Year by [[DSL Sport]]\n* '''2013:''' [[2013 FIVB Volleyball Men's U23 World Championship|FIVB U23 World Championship]] \u2013 Best Outside Spiker\n* '''2016:''' [[2016 Memorial of Hubert Jerzy Wagner|Memorial of Hubert Jerzy Wagner]] \u2013 Best Outside Spiker\n* '''2016:''' [[2016 Asian Men's Club Volleyball Championship|Asian Club Championship]] \u2013 Best Outside Spiker\n* '''2018:''' [[2018 FIVB Volleyball Men's Club World Championship|FIVB Club World Championship]] \u2013 Best Outside Spiker\n* '''2019:''' [[2019 Men's European Volleyball Championship|CEV European Volleyball Championship]] \u2013 Best Outside Spiker\n* '''2019:''' [[2019 Men's European Volleyball Championship|CEV European Volleyball Championship]] \u2013 Most Valuable Player \n* '''2019:''' CEV Male Volleyball Player of the Year<ref>{{cite news |title=Top achievements honoured at European Volleyball Gala |url=https://www.cev.eu/News.aspx?NewsID=29910&ID=1 |accessdate=25 October